## Why This Is Asked
Tests offline-first design, conflict resolution, and Android architecture (Room, WorkManager), plus privacy controls.

## Key Concepts
- Offline-first data model with Room encryption
- Vector clocks for per-conversation conflict resolution
- WorkManager pipelines with network constraints and retries

## Code Example
```kotlin
data class VectorClock(val map: MutableMap<String, Long>) {
  fun merge(other: VectorClock): VectorClock {
    val result = map.toMutableMap()
    for ((k, v) in other.map) {
      result[k] = maxOf(result.getOrDefault(k, 0L), v)
    }
    return VectorClock(result)
  }
}
```

