## Why This Is Asked
Tests familiarity with MVVM, Room, Retrofit, and offline-first UX. Focus on data flow, error handling, and testability.

## Key Concepts
- Room: Entity, DAO, migrations
- Retrofit: API interface, suspend functions
- MVVM: ViewModel + LiveData
- Offline-first: Cache-first, background sync

## Code Example
```kotlin
@Entity
data class Article(
  @PrimaryKey val id: String,
  val title: String,
  val body: String?,
  val updatedAt: Long
)

@Dao
interface ArticleDao {
  @Query("SELECT * FROM Article ORDER BY updatedAt DESC")
  fun getAll(): LiveData<List<Article>>

  @Insert(onConflict = OnConflictStrategy.REPLACE)
  suspend fun insertAll(articles: List<Article>)
}

interface ArticleApi {
  @GET("articles")
  suspend fun getArticles(): List<Article>
}
```

